Introduction

I.C.E (아이스) was a three-member girl group formed by HS Entertainment in 2015. Originally as four, they debuted on November 16, 2015 with their single "Over U".
Their name stands for "International Center of Issue". On July 20, 2022, the members announced the group's disbandment via Instagram.
